.TH "ep93xx_dma_alloc_chan_resources" 9 "ep93xx_dma_alloc_chan_resources" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ep93xx_dma_alloc_chan_resources \- allocate resources for the channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ep93xx_dma_alloc_chan_resources
.BI "(struct dma_chan *chan "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "chan" 12
channel to allocate resources
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Function allocates necessary resources for the given DMA channel and
returns number of allocated descriptors for the channel. Negative errno
is returned in case of failure.
